The paper deals with face recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed algorithm involves low rank representation and dictionary learning, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves experiments on public databases, which suggests a focus on multimedia (cs.MM) and potentially cybersecurity (cs.CR) as well.
